<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IFRS10_B38" base="F16126929" principles="no"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>B38</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 10"/><data name="paranum" value="B38"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS10_P0325">An investor can have power even if it holds less than a majority of the voting rights of an investee. An investor can have power with less than a majority of the voting rights of an investee, for example, through:</p><ol outputclass="static" id="IFRS10_L0031" base="F16126931" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS10_P0326" base="F16126932">a contractual arrangement between the investor and other vote holders (see <xref id="IFRS10_X0407" base="F16219023" href="IFRS10_gB39-B39.dita#IFRS10_gB39-B39/IFRS10_gB39-B39_TI">paragraph B39</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS10_P0327" base="F16126934">rights arising from other contractual arrangements (see <xref id="IFRS10_X0408" base="F16219024" href="IFRS10_gB40-B40.dita#IFRS10_gB40-B40/IFRS10_gB40-B40_TI">paragraph B40</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS10_P0328" base="F16126936">the investor’s voting rights (see <xref id="IFRS10_X0409" base="F16219108" href="IFRS10_gB41-B46.dita#IFRS10_gB41-B46/IFRS10_gB41-B46_TI">paragraphs B41–B45</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value> <p id="IFRS10_P0329" base="F16126941">potential voting rights (see <xref id="IFRS10_X0410" base="F16219109" href="IFRS10_gB47-B50.dita#IFRS10_gB47-B50/IFRS10_gB47-B50_TI">paragraphs B47–B50</xref>); or</p></li><li><li_value>(e)</li_value> <p id="IFRS10_P0330" base="F16126943">a combination of (a)–(d).</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>